cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper proposes a novel method for estimating socioeconomic indicators using natural language processing (NLP) techniques applied to geolocated Wikipedia articles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP and information retrieval. The paper also uses satellite imagery, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CY (Computers and Society). Additionally, the paper deals with data analysis and prediction, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.SD (Sound and Data).
